oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hatch Show Print 1968 Date Book
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hatch Show Print (Firm); Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet featuring the Hatch Show Print logo and address for a 1968 date book. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
